 "We are also planning a mass prayer service for the seven," said Rotich.
 The bodies were moved to mortuaries in Kericho and Uasin Gishu from Nakuru. The victims died when their car was involved in an accident at Kamara along Nakuru-Eldoret highway on Saturday night.Â 




